ement (July 1996-January 1997)\n|-\n|1997\n|''The Old Neighborhood''\n|Jolly\n|Broadway\n|-\n|2000\n|''Matters of the Heart''<ref>Isherwood, Christopher. [https://variety.com/2000/legit/reviews/patti-lupone-matters-of-the-heart-2-1200465434/ \"Review. ''Patti LuPone: Matters of the Heart''] ''Variety'', November 13, 2000</ref>\n|Herself\n|New York (Lincoln Center Beaumont Theater); Solo Concert\n|-\n|2000\n|''[[Sweeney Todd: The Demon Barber of Fleet Street|Sweeney Todd]]''<ref>[http://www.sondheimguide.com/concerts.html \"Sondheim Concerts\"] sondheimguide.com, accessed November 20, 2019</ref>\n|[[Mrs. Lovett]]\n|New York Philharmonic Concert\n|-\n|2001\n|''[[Noises Off]]''\n|Dotty Ottley\n|Broadway Revival\n|-\n|2002\n|''Runt of the Litter''\n|VO: National Anthem\n|\n|-\n|2002\n|''Anything Goes''<ref>[https://www.broadwayworld.com/shows/backstage.php?showid=3243 \" ''Anything Goes'' Concert\"] broadwayworld.com, accessed November 20, 2019</ref>\n|Reno Sweeney\n|Reunion Concert, Lincoln Center, Beaumont Theater\n|-\n|2003\n|''[[Passion (musical)|Passion]]''\n|Fosca\n|Regional Concert ([[Ravinia Festival]])\n|-\n|2004\n|''[[Can-Can (musical)|Can-Can]]''<ref>Miller, Mark. [https://www.theatermania.com/new-york/reviews/can-can_4378.html \"reviews. ''Can-Can''\"] \ntheatermania.com, February 13, 2004</ref>\n|La Mome Pistache\n|[[Encores!]] Staged Concert\n|-\n|2004\n|''[[Candide (operetta)|Candide]]''<ref>Portantiere, Michael. [https://www.theatermania.com/new-york-city-theater/reviews/candide_4694.html \"Review. ''Candide''] theatermania.com, May 10, 2004</ref>\n|Old Lady\n|New York Philharmonic Staged Concert\n|-\n|2004\n|''[[Sunday in the Park with George]]''<ref>Gans, Andrew. [http://www.playbill.com/article/mcdonald-lupone-cerveris-sunday-in-the-park-with-george-begins-sept-3-com-121614# \"McDonald-LuPone-Cerveris ''Sunday in the Park'' with George Begins Sept. 3\"] Playbill, September 3, 2004</ref>\n|Yvonne\n|Regional Concert ([[Ravinia Festival]])\n|-\n|2005\n|'