an\n| \n|-\n| 1993\n| ''[[Family Prayers]]''<ref>[http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/family_prayers/ ''Family Prayers''] rottentomatoes.com, accessed November 20, 2019</ref>\n| Aunt Nan\n| \n|-\n| 1999\n| ''[[The 24 Hour Woman]]''<ref>[https://www.allmovie.com/movie/the-24-hour-woman-v175634 \"''The 24 Hour Woman'' Overview\"] allmovie.com, accessed November 20, 2019</ref>\n| Joan Marshall\n| \n|-\n| 1999\n| ''[[Summer of Sam]]''<ref>[https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/summer_of_sam \" ''Summer of Sam'' Cast\"] rottentomatoes.com, accessed November 20, 2019</ref>\n| Helen\n| \n|-\n| 2000\n| ''[[State and Main]]''\n| Sherry Bailey\n| [[Florida Film Critics Circle Award for Best Cast]]<br />[[National Board of Review Award for Best Cast]]<br />[[Online Film Critics Society Award for Best Cast]]\n|-\n| 2001\n| ''[[Heist (2001 film)|Heist]]''\n| Betty Croft\n| \n|-\n| 2002\n| ''[[City by the Sea]]''\n| Maggie\n| \n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[Company (musical)|Company]]''<ref>[http://www.pbs.org/wnet/gperf/sondheims-company-with-the-new-york-philharmonic-about-the-show/1885/ \"''Company'' PBS Great Performances\"] pbs.com, accessed November 18, 2019</ref><ref>Gans, Andrew. [http://www.playbill.com/article/film-of-company-with-neil-patrick-harris-and-patti-lupone-airs-on-pbs-nov-8-com-211573# \"Film of ''Company'', With Neil Patrick Harris and Patti LuPone, Airs on PBS Nov. 8\"] Playbill, November 8, 2013</ref>\n| Joanne\n| Taped version of 2011 NY Philharmonic Concert, televised on PBS [[Great Performances]]\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[Parker (2013 film)|Parker]]''\n| Ascension\n| \n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[The Comedian (2016 film)|The Comedian]]''\n| Flo Berkowitz\n|\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Cliffs of Freedom]]''\n| Yia-Yia\n| \n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Last Christmas (film)|Last Christmas]]''\n| Joyce\n| \n|}\n\n===Television===\nSources: TCM<ref name=tcm/>; AllMovie<ref name=all/>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\"| Notes\n|-\n| 1976\n| ''The Time of Your Lif